Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{How many edible ones were there?}Có bao nhiêu con ăn được?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Take care of this, too.}Xử lý bên này nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Carry that first.}Bên này trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ugh, there they go again.}Phiền phức thật. Lại nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{They put themselves in the battle\Nand got themselves killed. It's astounding.}Tự đưa mình vào trận chiến và chết. Thiệt tình...
