Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{I saw, you know!}Tôi thấy rồi nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{You know, your brief return to the battlefield!}Hiếm lắm anh mới quay lại chiến trường!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{You saw on the monitors?}Cậu thấy trên màn hình à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's right. You looked so cool!}Phải đó! Anh ngầu ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{I bet it took you back to\Nyour days as a top ranker.}Quả nhiên anh muốn quay lại những ngày đứng top hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did you hear me?}Có nghe không đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Kaburagi?}Ủa? Kaburagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait, you aren't filling up on oxyone?}Khoan đã, anh chưa nạp Oxyone à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's up with him? Strange.}Anh ta bị gì vậy? Lạ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"Colossal Corporate Enterprise Solid Quake"}Tập đoàn Solid Quake
