Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"Personal Room"\NDammit.}Chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{The battlefield... never again...}Mình... đã hứa sẽ không tham gia nữa...
