Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, so cool!}Ngầu quá đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Skin shop?}Cửa hàng da?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is this place?}Cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, wait up!}Này, chờ cháu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{If the world must be rid of bugs,}Nếu thế giới phải loại bỏ lỗi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{she has to be eliminated.}thì con bé sẽ bị loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{If the world must be rid of bugs...}Nếu thế giới phải loại bỏ lỗi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{...that would mean she has no value.}...tức là con bé không có giá trị.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{But in that moment...}Nhưng trong khoảnh khắc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{But in that moment...}Nhưng trong khoảnh khắc đó...
